description: One look at Tyler Torro tells you that he is XXXtreme. Guy is an animal. Ferocious. Does everything full bore and with crazy intensity, often to the detriment of his own well being. Such is the case with his work out regimen, where Tyler maxes out and hurts his wrist. Luckily, Steven Daigle is there to take care of Tyler's pain and turn it into extreme pleasure.Enjoy!
title: WORKIN' IT OUT
